@host = http://localhost:5162
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1/consolidation
@merchantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### Get daily balance for today
GET {{baseUrl}}/2026-03-04
X-User-Id: {{merchantId}}

### Get daily balance for a specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/2026-03-01
X-User-Id: {{merchantId}}

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health

### OpenAPI spec
GET {{host}}/openapi/v1.json
